Package: SCM
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Subpixel Confusion Matrix
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Dainius", family = "Masiliunas", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "pastas4@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5654-1277"))
             )
Description: An implementation of the algorithm for calculating confusion
    matrices for fuzzy (fractional) land cover classes, including the associated
    uncertainties, as given in the paper by Silvan-Cardenas and Wang (2008)
    <doi:10.1016/j.rse.2007.07.017>. The operators to use for the agreement and
    disagreement cells are user-configurable, and the ones used in the paper are
    included.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests:
    lattice,
    gridExtra
License: GPL (>= 3)
BugReports: https://github.com/GreatEmerald/SCM/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
